This paper belongs to the field of computer security (cs.CR) as it focuses on understanding underground online forums that trade stolen financial data. Additionally, it may also fall under the category of cybercrime (cs.CY) as it deals with illegal activities conducted online. The paper also involves data analysis and monitoring, which could fall under the categories of social and information sciences (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
